## PRIORITIZED SOURCE ROADMAP

### Tier 1 — High Signal, Low Complexity, Free (Do These First)

These should be implemented before any scraping. RSS-accessible, enterprise-focused, directly name DSPs and SIs.

**1. DroneLife (dronelife.com)**
- RSS: `https://dronelife.com/feed/`
- Focus: Commercial drone deployments, partnerships, contracts, operator announcements
- Why it matters: Consistently covers named DSPs/SIs deploying hardware. Avoids consumer content. High precision for FlytBase target companies.
- Volume: ~5-15 new articles/week relevant to deployment signals
- Implementation: Direct RSS ingest → existing scoring pipeline

**2. Commercial UAV News (commercialuavnews.com)**
- RSS: `https://www.commercialuavnews.com/feed`
- Focus: Enterprise-only by design. Energy, construction, public safety, mining verticals.
- Why it matters: Best single source for DSP deployment announcements in target verticals. Named operators always mentioned.
- Volume: ~8-20 articles/week. Higher precision than GN.
- Implementation: Direct RSS ingest

**3. Unmanned Systems Technology (unmannedsystemstechnology.com)**
- RSS: `https://www.unmannedsystemstechnology.com/feed/`
- Focus: Technical deployments, contracts, system integrators. Strong SI coverage.
- Why it matters: SIs who build custom drone solutions are explicitly named. Contract wins and deployment milestones covered.
- Volume: ~10-25 articles/week

**4. DroneDJ (dronedj.com)**
- RSS: `https://dronedj.com/feed/`
- Focus: Mix of enterprise and consumer, but enterprise section is strong
- Why it matters: Covers BVLOS approvals, dock deployments, logistics partnerships — all high-value signals
- Caveat: Filter consumer/hobbyist content using existing scoring prompt (already calibrated)
- Volume: ~15-30 articles/week, ~30-40% enterprise relevant

**5. PR Newswire / Business Wire / GlobeNewswire — Keyword RSS**
- RSS patterns:
  - PRN: `https://www.prnewswire.com/rss/news-releases-list.rss` (keyword search via URL params)
  - GlobeNewswire: `https://www.globenewswire.com/RssFeed/subjectcode/20-Contracts+%26+Agreements` and similar subject feeds
- Why it matters: DSPs and SIs issue press releases when they win contracts, sign partnerships, or go live. These are first-party announcements — highest precision of any source. GN and NewsAPI both index these eventually, but PR wires give them 12-48h earlier.
- Caveat: Requires keyword filtering (drone, autonomous, UAV + dock/deployment) at ingest time

