### Tier 3 — Government Procurement Databases (High Precision, Requires Parsing)

These surface contracts before they appear in the press. A company winning a drone service tender = confirmed DSP. Highest-quality signal possible for public sector buyers.

**US Federal**
- SAM.gov ATOM feed: `https://sam.gov/api/prod/opps/v3/opportunities/search?...` (keyword: "drone services", "UAS", "unmanned aerial")
- Scope: Federal agencies, DoD (where permitted), DHS, DOE — all active buyers of drone inspection services

**UK**
- Contracts Finder: `https://www.contractsfinder.service.gov.uk/Published/Notices/PublicFeed/RSS` — keyword filterable
- Find a Tender (FTS) — post-Brexit replacement for OJEU

**EU**
- TED (Tenders Electronic Daily): `https://ted.europa.eu/TED/search/search.do` — keyword search API available
- Scope: All EU member states' public procurement. Energy, infrastructure, public safety all covered.

**Australia**
- AusTender (tenders.gov.au) — federal drone service contracts
- State procurement portals (NSW eTendering, VIC Tenders)

